  <brief_title>Double-blind, Placebocontrolled A Randomized Trial on the Efficacy of Herbal Galactogogues</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Herbal Galactogogues: a Double-blinded, Placebo-controlled Randomized Trial.</official_title>
