  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the effectiveness of a commercially available product
      containing a combination of Silybum marianum and Galega officinalis to support continuation
      or augmentation of breast milk production.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
